item.title: Prayer bpn13011 in Nalik
item.description: Saaule Nakmai! Saaule Nakmai! Fatuing a mun mamaangon a yaanakilaaing Sunum. Gu na viaat a divavun a vaamuzesing Sunum. Ma xa daxo tamon di valos a mun burburaaiing ma ngeiwulut Sunum. Saaule Nakmai a i naxaaming funfun sin naande ma fadikdik naande xu na varamaraat aang a vaamuzesing si naande. Saaule Nakmai! Gu na pen pengin pizin naande ma singsaxei Gu na valos naande wan a vamaravaas aang a rexaasing ma fananaam a mun mamaangon naande wan a nanaming.
